name: Pillow Cases: Toddler or Otherwise
description:
Perfect for adding a splash of color to a room, for toddler nap time at home or school or for cushioning an uncomfortable office chair.

Pillow Cases are 12 x 16 -other sizes available upon request.  Each one is handmade with envelope closure.  Pillow Forms are not included.  

Prewashed and Preshrunk. Machine Washable. Made from decor weight canvas.

MANY FABRIC CHOICES ARE AVAILABLE! email aimee@aimeealeene.com for current fabric choices.

name: Bright Rainbow Colors: Single Paci Clips
description:
100% Cotton and easy to use, these Paci Clips are compatible will Soothies and standard pacifiers.  They are easy to attach to little ones with one hand. Paci clips can be washed by clipping the ribbon to itself and enclosing in a lingerie bag.  Clips should not be used while child is asleep or unattended.

Many colors are available. Email aimee@aimeealeene.com for current choices.
